directions: ["Cut chicken into bite size pieces.", "Saute in oil until done. Combine soy sauce, oil, garlic and lemon juice.", "Add the cooked chicken and cut up lettuce, broccoli, tomatoes, cucumbers, walnuts and peppers.", "Add can of water chestnuts (drained).", "Toss with chicken mixture.", "Marinate overnight.", "Before serving, add the sesame seed."]
NER: ["tomatoes", "lemon juice", "salad oil", "soy sauce", "water chestnuts", "clove garlic", "chicken cutlets"]
